title: THURSDAY - Super Wildcard Weekend injury updates
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Super Wildcard Weekend injury updates
description:
Chase Young excited to face Tom Brady on Saturday (0:06), hear what Brady has to say about the matchup. We have a host of important injury updates including Jared Goff and Cooper Kupp (1:17), Saints wide receiver Michael Thomas (1:54), and Bills wide receiver Stefon Diggs (2:12). Lamar Jackson hoping to exercise his playoff demons (2:22) and we'll catch you up on the latest interviews (3:08) for head coaching vacancies
